seo: 用友U9,文件上传漏洞,插件检测
summary: 该插件用于检测用友U9系统是否存在PatchFile.asmx文件的任意文件上传漏洞，通过发送POST请求尝试上传文件并验证上传成功与否。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the Yongyou U9 system has an arbitrary file upload vulnerability in the PatchFile.asmx file by sending a POST request to attempt uploading a file and verifying if it succeeds.
